Test Description: we want to build a solution to hire the right people quickly. The development work of this solution is part of the solution. As a candidate, please contribute your idea and finish the assignment.

Definition of done:
1. Based on Test1, please setup a new URL /dog to display the picture of a random dog. 
2. The picture should be from the internet rather than a local file.
3. UT coverage > 80% if not 100%
4. Provide test evidence like screenshots to show the completion of 2 and 3.
